"visibility":"full","cve_ids":[],"singular_disclosure_disabled":true,"disclosed_at":"2021-05-06T06:30:27.734Z","bug_reporter_agreed_on_going_public_at":"2021-05-06T06:30:26.895Z","team_member_agreed_on_going_public_at":"2021-05-06T06:13:18.543Z","comments_closed?":false,"facebook_team?":false,"team_private?":false,"vulnerability_information":"## Summary:\n\nPentest leads should not be able to edit pentest summary report answers after submitting them.\n\n## Steps To Reproduce:\n\n1) After submitting the pentest summary report, try to edit it:\n\n{F1246327}\n\nYou can't. The form is disabled.\n\n2) Use the HTTP Request below (update `X-Auth-Token`, `Cookie` and the `pentestFormAnswerId`):\n\n```\nPOST /graphql HTTP/1.1\nHost: hackerone.com\nUser-Agent: Mozilla/5.0 (X11; Linux i686; rv:75.0) Gecko/20100101 Firefox/75.0\nAccept: */*\nAccept-Language: pt-BR,en-US;q=0.5\nAccept-Encoding: gzip, deflate\nReferer: https://hackerone.com/******************************************************************\ncontent-type: application/json\nX-Auth-Token: ******************************************************************\nContent-Length: 1498\nOrigin: https://hackerone.com\nDNT: 1\nConnection: close\nCookie: ******************************************************************\n\n{\"operationName\":\"UpdatePentestFormAnswer\",\"variables\":{\"pentestFormAnswerId\":\"******************************************************************\",\"content\":\"Blah blah blah\"},\"query\":\"mutation UpdatePentestFormAnswer($pentestFormAnswerId: ID!, $content: String!) {\\n  updatePentestFormAnswer(input: {pentest_form_answer_id: $pentestFormAnswerId, content: $content}) {\\n    was_successful\\n    pentest_form_answer {\\n      id\\n      content\\n      __typename\\n    }\\n    __typename\\n  }\\n}\\n\"}\n```\n\nThe pentest summary report will be edited.\n\n{F1246329}\n\n## Recommendation:\n\nShow an error instead of allowing the modification of pentest summary report answers.\n\n## Impact\n\nA pentest lead can modify the pentest summary report answers after submitting them to review.","weakness":{"id":106,"name":"Modification of Assumed-Immutable Data (MAID)"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[{"id":1246327,"file_name":"Captura_de_Tela_2021-03-29_a_s_02.35.46.png","expiring_url":"https://hackerone-us-west-2-production-attachments.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/tfqhhsjjw6379d3y5psovdgrk5f1?response-content-disposition=attachment%3B%20filename%3D%22Captura_de_Tela_2021-03-29_a_s_02.35.46.png%22%3B%20filename%2A%3DUTF-8%27%27Captura_de_Tela_2021-03-29_a_s_02.35.46.png\u0026response-content-type=image%2Fpng\u0026X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256\u0026X-Amz-Credential=ASIAQGK6FURQUYMBO5AB%2F20260429%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request\u0026X-Amz-Date=20260429T082243Z\u0026X-Amz-Expires=3600\u0026X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjECcaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJIMEYCIQCj5M3au%2FUKit%2FZjgGFQ0AJn8AbI3pPE3c1AwGr4pFIAwIhAMs0A0uwF2%2BDACnbkPxjpAntf5IJ43uI3FvbXIMSj9iyKroFCPD%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FwEQAxoMMDEzNjE5Mjc0ODQ5IgzggqolI9E%2Bi0ndrVYqjgUdLZdDxKX7heSvNdEzB3N7YO0uRzv3rrMocSqAHTaClWeRYXXnfkJOU64c%2FPvrXbh05mbOFBx5yOBgOFM9BuTj9Hdodcc4SF7BrHlhZt1e2oZMnArjhSSr%2Fk%2FSeY4Z9YqyBin9idJ%2Bav%2F4Zl44PkjqI2XfWHI270fclISRkaTOQ2Jbj06BUpnNnj%2FfkG%2BB02dydLBT5%2FQEku92arZQuN76KvDRYiUEBqTnt4QaQfthsvbw5FFbx2WwPp7FcO84jEiF85ddghyD20J3sLZc6aiPRG74U7uLS%2BHJVKhLA1ts2UcLXTFJKf2704TnXIKL9lsVZ%2FrX0oqyhN0fbFXXdRk%2B1F0VqS%2BKN2I6yEeIagwxN5UvgdlH6A0lGuUrOo0pQotWpnZMRbGmzu365fynnbsxyT9Q7l741rdJyjhYeydbxv1rklKtb6%2B6gtzinHHap0qGsen2NtrKrbWcf40JYbwLcdKeR8HzATdAlZyYNu8sEemUM3FQRjb%2Fb0AujdQ5fr%2FHg1MydKzJqchw%2B6rJNwnIofBhrDQWwOOwhf3GOu1IQQx5lOKPd6i8F3NF7pHLOyyubwAvfqBOSK07KrdRU2gUfHf8Dj3lVs30Zt%2BIs6Hdw5JCR%2FvY972pOqQseBkqngMsM5ECDXgsvaIdRsxoJqWmb7XfYoGuKrI%2Bq1N7fbO5GJgvZ7Wx%2F3N7%2BGMlUmsYNfM02gUJk8755Y4Cyp2iy2Srg%2FRorUbj5m9miGoiGSm2ZUM2OjwYMkTw%2FRWun3iWWqPc0HzfKsJZyPxZofW96TlIh27yXsm9rKzC0%2BlvvGe8FaGvdBY78jT5Mf4EFvQ1nNEwUqXbKEDenzracmBFGNVPtw%2BX%2BMvAQFr0Hi8I